IMAPAccount raffaele.nickp@gmail.com
Host imap.gmail.com
User raffaele.nickp@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass Raffaele.nickp@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore personal-gmail-remote
Account raffaele.nickp@gmail.com

MaildirStore personal-gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/raffaele.nickp@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/raffaele.nickp@gmail.com/Inbox

Channel personal-gmail-default
Far :personal-gmail-remote:
Near :personal-gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* !Sent* !Drafts* !Trash*
Create Near
Remove Near
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel personal-gmail-sent
Far :personal-gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :personal-gmail-local:Sent
Create Near
Remove Near
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel personal-gmail-trash
Far :personal-gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Near :personal-gmail-local:Trash
Create Near
Remove Near
SyncState *
Expunge Both

Channel personal-gmail-drafts
Far :personal-gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Near :personal-gmail-local:Drafts
Create Near
Remove Near
SyncState *
Expunge Both

# Get all the channels together into a group.
Group personal-gmail
Channel personal-gmail-default
Channel personal-gmail-sent
Channel personal-gmail-trash
Channel personal-gmail-drafts
